-------------------------------------------------
Pedestrian Detection application (Viola & Jones algorithm adapted from OpenCV, CUDA implementation based on the C version implemented by T. Petrisor)
-------------------------------------------------

CONTENT of this application distribution

	violajones.cu 		-- source file in CUDA
	violajones.h		-- header file
	classifier.txt 		-- input test data needed for running the benchmark (do not remove)
	person_015.pgm 		-- input test data needed for running the benchmark (do not remove)
	Makefile
        cutil.h,libcutil.a      -- utility library from NVIDIA's CUDA SDK for reproducibility with our experiments (newer versions can be used)
     

HOW TO COMPILE and RUN the application

make
make run

